## Simple XML Dictionary Resource Provider README
   https://github.com/kevinblake/XML-Dictionary-Resource-Provider

## Introduction

   A simple XML resource provider for .NET Localisation / Translation.  This is an
   alternative to .resx files for more human readable files and extensibility.
   More providers can easily be added for databases, web services or other file
   formats.

